    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><div n="1" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/>
                <expan><abbr>Imp</abbr><ex>eratori</ex></expan> Caesari divi Nervae <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>ilio</ex></expan> <lb n="2"/>Nervae Traiano optimo <lb n="3"/><expan><abbr>Aug</abbr><ex>usto</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Germ</abbr><ex>anico</ex></expan> Dacico <expan><abbr>pont</abbr><ex>ifici</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>max</abbr><ex>imo</ex></expan> <lb n="4"/><expan><abbr>trib</abbr><ex>unicia</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>pot</abbr><ex>estate</ex></expan> XVII <expan><abbr>imp</abbr><ex>eratori</ex></expan> VI c<supplied reason="lost"><expan><abbr>o</abbr><ex>n</ex></expan></supplied><expan><abbr>s</abbr><ex>uli</ex></expan> VI <expan><abbr>p</abbr><ex>atri</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>p</abbr><ex>atriae</ex></expan> </ab></div><div n="2" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> <expan><abbr>L</abbr><ex>ucius</ex></expan> Laelius <expan><abbr>L</abbr><ex>uci</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>ilius</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Cla</abbr><ex>udia</ex></expan> Proculus <lb n="2"/><expan><abbr>t</abbr><ex>estamento</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>ieri</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>i</abbr><ex>ussit</ex></expan> epuloque dedicari
            </ab></div></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Die Inschriften gehörten ursprünglich zum Trajanstor. Kaiserinschrift (a): über 2 nebeneinanderliegende Tafeln hinweglaufend; vermutlich von der Attica; Reste von roter Farbe in den Buchstaben. Stifterinschrift (b): über 2 nebeneinanderliegende Tafeln (74 x 294 x 30 cm) hinweglaufend; vielleicht vom Gebälk über dem Bogendurchgang; Buchstabenhöhe 12 cm. Hedera in Inschrift b, Z. 2. (B): Inschrift a: Kurilić: Z. 1: Ne[r]vae; Liebl - Wilberg; AE 1908; Kurilić: Z. 4: co(n)s(uli).</p>
            </div>
